Li Lab


Exploring Life’s Molecular Mysteries


We are an interdisciplinary research group at [University Name] dedicated to understanding fundamental biological processes and developing novel therapeutic approaches. Our research combines molecular biology, computational methods, and advanced imaging to solve complex biological problems.



